Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.83,0:01:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久別的亞加瑪傳來通話\n竟然是求救呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.51,0:01:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為它正受到敵人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.32,0:01:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為比查的奮鬥\n額外增加了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.39,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了…\n波蕾又感應到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.57,0:01:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了!一定又是古利明在附近\n所以波蕾她才有感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.16,0:02:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十三話 都柏林的午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自動操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,改變軌道\n咦,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2的修補工作完成\n辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開,我看不到前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.98,0:02:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開  你在幹什麼?艾莉\n這些要本人自己選取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.07,0:02:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些是幹什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服的兩者在造\n來自己選擇與不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.68,0:02:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩,好美,一片綠油油的\n這是森林吧 這是大陸哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這也不是自然造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?森林是自己所造的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.51,0:02:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜,歐洲的森林從\n前世紀開始全是人工所造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.13,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那和殖民地一樣嘛\n對,因為人口太多,不管的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全會變成像撒哈拉沙漠一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才移民到宇宙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,不用工作時請選取衣物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也是,這個要丟掉的吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.39,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,你也真是的\n可是這不是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為父親的別這樣說\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,航道要怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改道向西\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後還是沒人能駕駛那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,沒人可以支撐到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.02,0:03:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為它是以意志去控制\n這個我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.05,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那個是給古利明的補給嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.41,0:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,選取了亞里斯去負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞里斯嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和桑多拉會合地點已確認\n好,是和預定一樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞里斯大人,雲下有不明物體\n什麼?是飛機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不是,是亞加瑪!\n怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.29,0:04:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻打它,我們不只是運送貨物\n還有義務護衛貨物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍飛還沒組合好\n沒有時間了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.47,0:04:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼男人不幫忙?\n這是女人的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?亞當斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.23,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷調查已完成\n想取勝就應該重用波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她有克服緊急事故的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不只是是因為教導所導致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,為何改變方向?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是要去在挪威的\n加拉帕基地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已改向西行\n為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情變更?\n是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒必要一一說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長你總該見見妻子和子女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是活著遲早能見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(只要是活著...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(捷度...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.78,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?波蕾\n波蕾不能偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦?\n夠了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾!\n喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是非去都柏林不可\n都柏林?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是英國的勢力範圍\n去展示波蕾的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.20,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,不要擅自走動\n你誤會什麼而隨便動怒阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到竟然能帶亞加瑪作手信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.26,0:06:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞里斯大人,增援物品\n以照桑多拉所說準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以龐大的臉出現!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.42,0:06:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照計劃,去引敵人至最近距離\n出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艦長為了調查波蕾\n而去都柏林嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是次要\n你知道都柏林有一個秘密據點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地球聯邦高官的所在地嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!有戰機急速接近\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是哪一方的\n快調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.34,0:06:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼變扭起來?波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.29,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾\n不要,捷度認為我代替莉娜死比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會這樣想\n騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幫我重新疊好\n現在沒時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾她?\n逃走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你為責任而死\n我會高興嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明和莉娜一樣關心捷度你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛\n伊萊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼?\n有敵機來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.49,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒辦法一個人收拾敵人的\n比查,駕駛終端核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,是飛龍\n是由吉翁派來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出出擊命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機已經出動\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事波蕾嗎?\n她為何知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們查出前\n她已經發覺到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人也能打倒敵人\n你不是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.93,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,別想獨自一人應付\n太逞強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,我獨自戰死也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我可不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派出三流貨色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我死的話捷度就\n別死啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾擅自戰鬥,我或誰都不會高興\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼,行動模式總是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一點!\n比查,背後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,快合體阿\n我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.13,0:09:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溝通很快\n發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直和三流貨色糾纏\n亞加瑪會逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在附近\n合體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,一併攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在迅速接近\n不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!對方應該不能久戰\n先退避好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照做!\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,合體吧\n以後的交給捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?亞加瑪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏嗎?很接近哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟專程逃到下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別窮追不捨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯!捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,你和捷度在談話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡馬,避開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.15,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發光了,敵艦方向\n還沒被擊落,快避開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾真了不起,救了亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你們在嗎?已經結束了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.15,0:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到一場小戰就毀壞了噴射機\n臭亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看制服就知道\n我不是可疑之輩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪一位?\n可以的話請說出官銜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.95,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,艾莉,好像不夠呢?\n喂,聽到嗎?咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看穿了\n看穿了,看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.52,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?\n我說過購物等一下再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得不用檢查就能自由活動\n等等..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好呢,無拘無束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.89,0:12:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好落後\n這是什麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個鎮很落後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不在都市降落?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在都市降落會暴露亞加瑪行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.22,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直行就到挪威\n而且加拉帕也在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說這裏的醫生比較好\n我沒病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你時常感覺到不舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且真的沒事時你就可以外出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是..\n別但是了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個嗎?\n布拉度艦長要去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.24,0:13:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這一帶吧?  那不是私人住所嗎?\n聽說聯邦高官是在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦的大人在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.23,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快回來,波蕾你要乖乖去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不護送她去不行吧\n/好!   捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.79,0:13:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正是季節\n吃的豪華點也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但過肥就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提督其實我還抽煙了\n這不太好哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.92,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官,我帶客人來了\n客人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.68,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了\n我們正在用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是亞加瑪的艦長布拉度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪?\n為何不早說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亞加瑪的艦長就有問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.03,0:14:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有問題,布柆度艦長\n你是反對我們的和平策略吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.42,0:14:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將西多斯裏送給哈曼\n就是你們的和平策略嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.63,0:14:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼提出的條件簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭就能完結不是就能夠和平嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.82,0:14:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西多斯裏是殘暴的沙比家的起祥地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.76,0:15:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這麼做是助長新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼到了到了西多斯裏就能心息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.62,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦的工作不就是抑止戰爭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.23,0:15:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她想佔領各星系只是無聊傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.21,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解散亞加瑪船員,解除武裝吧\n怎樣?你也坐下來喝一杯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有新鮮的蔬果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道自己在說什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能吃飯還要明白什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.42,0:15:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在地球養尊處優,能明白什麼\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會知道哈曼是怎樣的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來人..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.15,0:15:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是以那麼難過的心情再戰鬥\n莉娜也死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我們貪圖戰鬥?\n住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是像你們什麼也不做\n這世界才這麼混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度,他是你的部下吧\n一個小孩子這麼大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來收取污穢的衣物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了\n不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.31,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一醫科的多雷濟請聽二線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一醫科的多雷濟請聽二線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請叫下一位\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在走廊上跑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那女孩身上\n有種熟悉的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那氣味是亞加瑪?\n不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.57,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?\n單憑布拉度艦長的申請書不被接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你不肯吧?\n我沒什麼不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,伊萊來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.94,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧..捷度呢?\n還沒回來  咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.45,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒來?是回了亞加瑪了嗎?\n或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.39,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他發生了什麼事?\n這市鎮感覺凌亂,無法知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你也來幫忙阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查努力就好了\n那女人  波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.32,0:17:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人,很感謝\n你聽取我的索取武器的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.48,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這是你幫我運回的謝禮,隨你喜歡去做吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已準備好了\n好,去吧亞里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪應該到了都柏林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最新情報呢?\n好像沒有進都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在都柏林有聯邦的人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們出去,困著我們也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.35,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,困我們在這裏打算餓死我們吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能吧..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也不會一直留在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在乾等下去\n亞加瑪可能會被解除武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事!\n攻擊?有敵來襲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊要盡量分散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之中有大使館\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們見到MS了吧?\n有兩架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,貨物稍後再拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.82,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但捷度還在都市內\n咦,沒帶布拉度艦長回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點還擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏戰鬥會損壞我的產業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭亞加瑪,不在都市在哪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去救援..\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒受太大損傷\n花小姐,對不起要你做這工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我自己要求的\n讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,外面有人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.51,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放我們出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想將我們變成炭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.85,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去...\n開門阿!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.10,0:20:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡阿\n有人在裏面阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人嗎?有人在裏面阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音我認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.88,0:20:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時借用ZZ高達等捷度回來再換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,引誘敵人到海邊或山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說也會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是剛才的傢伙\n對方也是兩艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都柏林又不是軍事區竟然用MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了,亞加瑪在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吸不了,  艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,連地面也佈滿濃煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎?有的話請回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.41,0:21:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有阿,但出不去\n想想辦法阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,我試試請退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還支持的下去嗎?\n真丟臉,但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.53,0:21:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聲音我認識的,是誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.25,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是艦長,還有捷度\n艦長?是花.園麗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯.我是花.園麗\n請快點,這棟樓很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.01,0:21:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝了...捷度快上去\n我沒問題的,艦長先上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是花嗎?\n和加美尤一起的花園.麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發了\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬴亞加瑪在附近嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在山的另一邊\n可以載我們去嗎?\n當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.50,0:22:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花小姐,為何你會在這個市鎮??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.33,0:22:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也正想問你們,為何在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.96,0:22:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了被濃煙所熏落淚而來的
